dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for the south shores of Raritan and Sandy Hook Bays, from the mouth of Cheesequake Creek to Highland Bridge across Shrewsbury River, New Jersey
dc_description_s: Two copies of map showing pierhead and bulkhead lines for the south shores of Raritan and Sandy Hook Bays. Copy one is the original drawn in January, 1892. Copy two, drawn on June 10, 1913, shows modifications of pierhead and bulkhead lines in Keyport, N.J.
